This learning path enables you to leverage your existing Tableau skills to create power data-driven reports and dashboards in Power BI. But before you put in the time, effort and money $$$...shouldn't you ask yourself "Is Power BI Certification Even Worth It?"  I am going to tell you 3 reasons you should and 3 reasons you shouldn't take these exams.
